Package org.biojava.nbio.structure.gui

Class WrapLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.FlowLayout
      • org.biojava.nbio.structure.gui.WrapLayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayoutManager, Serializable
    public class WrapLayout
extends FlowLayout
    FlowLayout subclass that fully supports wrapping of components. Originally written by Rob Camick https://tips4java.wordpress.com/2008/11/06/wrap-layout/
    See Also:

      • WrapLayout

        public WrapLayout​(int align)

        Parameters:

      • WrapLayout

        public WrapLayout​(int align,
                  int hgap,
                  int vgap)
        Creates a new flow layout manager with the indicated alignment and the indicated horizontal and vertical gaps.

        The value of the alignment argument must be one of WrapLayout, WrapLayout, or WrapLayout.

        Parameters:
        align - the alignment value
        hgap - the horizontal gap between components
        vgap - the vertical gap between components
